HOTAI MOTOR CO February Sales Fall 10.28% (Table) : 2207 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-03-10T06:31:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/hotai-motor-co-february-sales-fall-10-28-table-2207-tt.html
HOTAI MOTOR CO said unconsolidated sales
in February fell 10.28% to NT$5,661,859,000 from NT$6,310,680,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  2/2011           2/2010
Sales           5,661,859        6,310,680   
YOY%             -10.28%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           18,835,343       14,343,118  
YOY%              31.32% 
=================================================================
 